title: COVID-19 Advisory Board
added: There are thirteen members of the COVID-19 advisory board, appointed by [[President-elect of the United States|president-elect of the United States]] [[Joe Biden]]. Three of the members, [[David A. Kessler]], [[Vivek Murthy]] and [[Marcella Nunez-Smith]], serve as co-chairs.
